(1, 'Baker\'s Art', '667967269776c.png', 'Choose from our selection of cakes, cupcakes, pastries, and cookies for a fully customized spread for your lunch or dinner event. Our Pastry Chef will work closely with you to create a menu that suits your requirements for any occasion. Contact us for more information. At the Baker\'s Art patisserie, we are constantly pushing our imagination and creativity to new heights to bring you exciting new additions of tasty artisan cakes and pastries.', '20:40:00', '2024-07-05', 120, 1),
(2, 'The Brownies Project', '668167448af6d.jpg', 'Try a different kind of brownies with several different topping. Join us now to get the early bird price !', '10:15:00', '2024-07-30', 45, 1),
(3, 'Master Baking Pastry Program', '66816ae3e6012.jpeg', '10-Week Professional Master Baking Program and we have room for you!', '10:30:00', '2024-07-05', 1500, 1);

